Package anydev

Class Column_Double

java.lang.Object
anydev.Column_Double
All Implemented Interfaces:
Column
public class Column_Double extends Object implements Column
Define a column of double (or float) data (either for input or output data) Represents the metadata definition of a single column in a dataset (i.e. name but also restrictions, conditions, defaults...) This class does NOT store actual data values for the column.
Since:
v1.0.0
